fields.name: Status
fields.formula: if(field('Actual revenue') > field('Revenue target'),'🟢 Goal reached',if(field('Actual + Pipeline') >= field('Revenue target'),'🔵 On track',if(field('Actual + Pipeline + 10%') >= field('Revenue target'),'🟠 At risk','🔴 Off track')))

fields.name: Count accounts in pipeline
fields.formula: count(filter(lookup('Opportunities','Yearly deal size'),and(totext(lookup('Opportunities','Status')) != 'Deal closed won', totext(lookup('Opportunities','Status')) != 'Deal closed lost')))

fields.name: Deal size in pipeline
fields.formula: sum(filter(lookup('Opportunities','Yearly deal size'),and(totext(lookup('Opportunities','Status')) != 'Deal closed won', totext(lookup('Opportunities','Status')) != 'Deal closed lost')))

fields.name: Total closed + pipeline
fields.formula: field('Closed deals revenue') + field('Deal size in pipeline')
